trans-unit.source: Represents a <xref href="System.Windows.Media.GeneralTransform"></xref> that is a composite of the transforms in its <xref href="System.Windows.Media.GeneralTransformCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en <xref href="System.Windows.Media.GeneralTransform"> </xref> som er en kombinasjon av transformeringer i den <xref href="System.Windows.Media.GeneralTransformCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Use the GeneralTransformGroup class when you want to apply multiple general transforms to single object.
trans-unit.target: Bruk GeneralTransformGroup klassen når du vil bruke flere generelle transformeringer enkelt objekt.
